{"tid":1286751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於阻止選舉主任DQ區議員候選人的一些資訊及建議","createTime":"2019-07-05T03:04:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T15:35:45.000Z","uid":37592,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f9661292be19dabcdc9273f0ef2107dd153f1f4b","tid":1286751,"uid":37592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T03:04:06.000Z","msg":"發夢時同個前AO朋友傾開呢個問題，佢話SEND信去選舉事務處作用不大，因為DQ候選人唔係佢地既決定，選舉事務處亦無法左右選舉主任的決定(選舉事務處入面係一班EO，選舉主任係AO)，所以要做既話，除左SEND信去選舉事務處，更應該SEND去稍後會公佈負責的選舉主任，因為如果萬一佢地唔回覆投訴，技術上我地可以向選舉事務委員會投訴，如果委員會認為有需要可能會介入處理，這會對有關AO做成一定麻煩，所以<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家可以係選舉主任名單公佈後直接把我們的訴求EMAIL俾呢一班AO</span></span></strong>，令佢地有所顧忌<br />\n<br />\n我無野講!我無野講!我無野講!我無野講!我無野講!"},{"pid":"76853cb338b80b02e641303f3407d11014a98eb7","tid":1286751,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T05:53:18.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"40fa2417c6f5a0801ea73a3ea1d761b4f4075678","tid":1286751,"uid":32307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T06:12:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f048d4905e3ff3890396e5dbb752a775f936c5b","tid":1286751,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T00:22:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0e5428fd236163880b198a8e62401ced8122619","tid":1286751,"uid":18692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T05:32:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/223783954322429/posts/2576488119051989?s=575092502\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F223783954322429%2Fposts%2F2576488119051989%3Fs%3D575092502&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=566d0c57\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/223783954322429/posts/2576488119051989?s=575092502</a><br />\n可以參考呢個範本<br />\n一定要加減內容"},{"pid":"56ba1728a53d00d40ec3434a295704be3326cd61","tid":1286751,"uid":18692,"like":0,"disl